Kate Florence Spurrell (March 1886 - c.1968) bụ onye otu ọrụ aka na Britain na onye na-ahụ maka mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya.
A Amụrụ na Devonport, Devon, England, Spurrell ghọrọ onye nkuzi ụlọ akwụkwọ na Plymouth wee sonye na Liberal Party na National Union of Teachers (NUT)
A họpụtara ya ịbụ onye isi nke NUT, wee jee ozi dị ka onye isi oche ya na 1922.
ILP jikọtara ya na Labour Party, na na ntuli aka izugbe nke 1924, Spurrell guzoro na Totnes maka Labour, mana were naanị 6.1% nke votu ahụ
A họpụtara ya ọzọ na 1929, mgbe ọ mụbara òkè vootu ya ruo 12.9%.  N'afọ ahụ, a họpụtara ya na ILP's National Administrative Council (NAC), na-anọchite anya South West England.
Maka ntuli aka izugbe nke 1931, ndị Camborne Constituency Labour Party họpụtara Spurrell dị ka onye ndoro-ndoro ochichi ha
Ndị ILP kwadoro ya, mana onye isi mba Labour Party jụrụ ịkwado ya
N'agbanyeghị nke a, o were 24.5% nke votu na ebe atọ siri ike
O guzoro ọzọ na ntuli aka izugbe nke 1935, mana n'oge a megidere onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Labour Party, wee were naanị 1.9% nke votu ahụ..
Spurrell tụfuru oche ya na ILP's NAC na 1938, mana ọ nọgidere na-arụsi ọrụ ike na nnọkọ ahụ n'ime 1950s
N'afọ 1965, a gbara ya ajụjụ ọnụ maka BBC Home Service maka ahụmịhe ya nke iguzo dị ka onye ndoro-ndoro ILP na 1920s..
